OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FAnd so it has begun. The United States
OL,7,Fand Israel are once again carrying out
OL,8,Fstrikes on Iran.
OL,10,FThese are not small strikes. It seems
OL,11,Fany thought that this operation might
OL,12,Fopen with limited action to force
OL,13,FIran's hand at the negotiating table
OL,14,Fwere misplaced.
OL,16,FThis has been on the table officially
OL,17,Fsince January when President Trump
OL,18,Ftold Iranian protestors that help was
OL,19,Fcoming.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
