OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FIn reality it has been coming since
OL,7,Fthe last round of active conflict came
OL,8,Fto an end in June last year when a
OL,9,Fceasefire was declared in the 12 day
OL,10,Fwar.
OL,12,FThen, like now, talks for peace were
OL,13,Funderway, when the war began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
