OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FThe attacks will come as no surprise
OL,7,Fin Tehran, when I was there at the end
OL,8,Fof last year senior Iranian government
OL,9,Fministers were telling me they knew
OL,10,Fanother attack was coming and they
OL,11,Fwere prepared this time. They warned
OL,12,Fthere would be no hesitation in their
OL,13,Fresponse and no shock like was
OL,14,Fexperienced at the start of the war
OL,15,Flast June.
OL,17,FThis time it will be seen as
OL,18,Fexistential.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
