OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772301852
OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FAt senior levels they believe Israel
OL,7,Fsees this as a once in a century
OL,8,Fopportunity to destroy the nation of
OL,9,FIran, to weaken it beyond survival in
OL,10,Fthe quest for a "greater Israel". That
OL,11,Fview will guide their response as much
OL,12,Fas any.
OL,14,FThe American intervention has been
OL,15,Fdelivered in an all too familiar
OL,16,Fmanner, through an aerial bombardment
OL,17,Fof missiles and munitions, another
OL,18,Fmassive American military operation in
OL,19,Fa foreign country. History teaches the
OL,20,Fdangers of this moment.
OL,26,@rD@QOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
