PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772301852
OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FIt is not clear what the aim is - is
OL,7,Fthis an attempt to neutralise any
OL,8,Fnuclear capacity?
OL,10,FThey said that had been done last
OL,11,Fyear. Is this an attempt to topple the
OL,12,FIranian administration? That is a very
OL,13,Fdifficult challenge with an air war.
OL,14,FIs this the help that President Trump
OL,15,Fpromised protestors on January 13? It
OL,16,Fis difficult to predict right now
OL,17,Fwhether this "help" will bring the
OL,18,Fchange those who took to the streets
OL,19,Fand died in their thousands sought or
OL,20,Fif it is simply little more than false
OL,21,Fhope from a false friend.
OL,26,@yD@NOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
