OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FExternal military force in domestic
OL,12,Fpolitical crises rarely strengthens
OL,13,Fthose it claims to support. More often
OL,14,Fit hardens the hand of the state,
OL,15,Ffractures the opposition and turns a
OL,16,Fdomestic struggle into a geopolitical
OL,17,Fone.
OL,19,FSpeaking a few days ago with a senior
OL,20,Fgovernment figure the message was the
OL,21,Fsame and unambiguous.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
