OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772301852
OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FAny attack on Iran would be viewed as
OL,7,Fan existential threat and the response
OL,8,Fwould be fitting of that threat. It
OL,9,Fwould matter not whether the attack
OL,10,Fwas described or delivered as limited,
OL,11,Funlimited, surgical or kinetic.
OL,13,FBut it was also clear Iran, or
OL,14,Fcertainly parts of its government,
OL,15,Fwished to talk with the US, to
OL,16,Fnavigate a way forward. The WhatsApps
OL,17,Fhave gone backwards and forwards
OL,18,Fsince. "We will pursue peace until the
OL,19,Fvery last moment," a senior Iranian
OL,20,Ffigure told me, however it looks like
OL,21,Fthat opportunity has now passed.
OL,26,@zD@HOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
