OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FThe risks now are manifold.
OL,8,FThe consequences will not just be felt
OL,9,Fwithin Iran's borders. This is one of
OL,10,Fthe most heavily armed, powerful
OL,11,Fnations on the planet with the power
OL,12,Fto affect life globally. Their first
OL,13,Ftargets without question Israel, US
OL,14,Fassets and allies in the region. I
OL,15,Fknow that Jordan in particular has
OL,16,Fbeen warned of the dangers of getting
OL,17,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
