OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FThe UK has been warned about being
OL,7,Fparty to what is seen as a quest by
OL,8,Fthe US and Israel. Should they be
OL,9,Fdeemed to be part of this, at some
OL,10,Fpoint UK assets would also be at risk.
OL,11,FThe Iranian view, "Do they want an
OL,12,Fattack on Iran to be the cement
OL,13,Fbetween the UK and the USA with the
OL,14,Fpotential risks of that?"
OL,26,@sD@SOUvD@YO]
