OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FAs such expect a potential response
OL,7,Ffrom Iran's allies and proxies. Yes
OL,8,Fthey are weakened in recent years, but
OL,9,Fthey are not a spent force. Hezbollah
OL,10,Fin Lebanon, militias in Iraq and
OL,11,FSyria, the Houthis in Yemen are still
OL,12,Fwell armed and pose huge danger.
OL,13,FHezbollah will determine the scale of
OL,14,Fthe attack and may hold back initially
OL,15,Fbut if this is seen as an attack on
OL,16,Fthe Supreme Leader they will become
OL,17,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
