OL,3,CUS and Israeli strikes on Iran signal
OL,4,Ca dangerous new chapter
OL,6,FAnd brace for the possibility that
OL,7,Fshipping through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,8,Fbecomes vulnerable. This is where a
OL,9,Fsignificant portion of global shipping
OL,10,Fand global energy supply flows. Even a
OL,11,Flittle disruption will have huge
OL,12,Fimpact on markets, economies and
OL,13,Ftherefore the cost of your heating and
OL,14,Ffood.
OL,16,FThat, however, will be the least of
OL,17,Fthe worry for those now in the line of
OL,18,Ffire braced for days of war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
